*SYNOPSIS Symbols from the memory layout of the BBC Micro MOS 1.20.

; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ROM Header Addresses

romStartAddress                 @ $8000        ;
romLanguageEntry                @ $8000        ;
romServiceEntry                 @ $8003        ;
romTypeByte                     @ $8006        ;
romCopyrightOffsetPointer       @ $8007        ;
romTitleString                  @ $8009        ;

